  "text": "A seemingly natural way of salvaging homoscedastic methods is to test the assumption that there is homoscedasticity. But six studies summarized in [CITATION_1] found that this strategy is unsatisfactory. Presumably situations are encountered where this is not the case, but it is difficult and unclear how to determine when such situations are encountered.",
